text: Samuel Troilius, born 22 May 1706 in Stora Skedvi, Sweden, dead 18 January 1764 in Uppsala, Sweden was a Swedish Lutheran clergyman. He served as the Church of Sweden Archbishop of Uppsala from 1758 until his death 1764. == References == Category:1706 births Category:1764 deaths Category:Archbishops of Uppsala
title: Samuel Troilius
